name: - IN A MINUTE, I WILL WAKE UP.
description:
In the intergalactic and futuristic world of 2002, technology development has become mankind's ultimate goal and hybrid humans are the next step in our evolution. What would it be like to wake up in this alien utopia?

Featured in the first issue of CYBR Magazine as part of the "2002" photo series, 2018. 
Shot at UNB - Brasília, Brazil. 
TW: @maxupgradeduh / IG: @maxupgrade / Model: @igorandom.
